data.title: The Diocese of Karnataka South
data.text:
This web page is http://www.karnatakasouth.anglican.org, which belongs to the Diocese of Karnataka South, which is part of the Anglican Domain. The Diocese of Karnataka South is part of the Province of South India. The Church of South India is an autonomous Church in the Anglican Communion

Not every Anglican diocese worldwide has a Web page yet. The web page that you are now reading is operated by the Society of Archbishop Justus as a placeholder until The Diocese of Karnataka South is prepared to have its own page. The Society operates the domain ANGLICAN.ORG in trust for the Anglican Communion; karnatakasouth.anglican.org, a subdomain issued to the Diocese of Karnataka South, is part of what is being held in trust.

If you represent the staff of The Diocese of Karnataka South and would like to learn how to take ownership of the name karnatakasouth.anglican.org please see http://anglican.org/domain/ and read about the naming plan.
